WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:08.020
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.in Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:08.180 --> 00:00:11.020
(A dilapidated temple on the frontier)

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:08.280
What are you trying to do?

00:01:09.799 --> 00:01:10.879
Sir,

00:01:11.159 --> 00:01:14.079
you're the Grand General of Cavalry
appointed by the Emperor.

00:01:15.439 --> 00:01:17.200
You fear no death,

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:19.959
yet would you fear a mere woman?

00:01:20.599 --> 00:01:23.680
Are you a human or a ghost?

00:01:26.719 --> 00:01:28.000
My name is Qing Yan.

00:01:29.239 --> 00:01:30.480
I was entrusted

00:01:30.840 --> 00:01:32.359
to heal your wounds.

00:01:39.879 --> 00:01:41.239
Who sent you?

00:01:53.140 --> 00:01:53.959
(Memorial Tablet of Beloved Friend, Su Hua)

00:01:53.959 --> 00:01:56.560
(Memorial Tablet of Beloved Friend, Su Hua)
Though you couldn't save Ms. Su,

00:01:57.280 --> 00:02:00.519
you and she shared deep affection.

00:02:01.120 --> 00:02:02.840
She couldn't bear

00:02:02.840 --> 00:02:04.560
to see you die.

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:11.000
While she met a tragedy,

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:12.919
you rose to glory

00:02:12.919 --> 00:02:14.199
and are soon to wed the princess.

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:16.919
Such betrayal.

00:02:47.060 --> 00:02:51.100
=Destiny of the General's Bride=

00:02:51.540 --> 00:02:54.500
=Episode 1=

00:02:55.300 --> 00:03:00.140
(Xiao Residence)

00:03:01.900 --> 00:03:03.719
(Three days later)

00:03:03.719 --> 00:03:05.199
What exactly do you want?

00:03:06.879 --> 00:03:08.479
I want to marry into the Xiao family

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:11.960
and become your wife.

00:03:13.800 --> 00:03:14.639
Absurd.

00:03:15.520 --> 00:03:16.400
Why should I take you?

00:03:16.800 --> 00:03:17.800
Like I said,

00:03:18.639 --> 00:03:20.520
not only will you not harm me,

00:03:20.960 --> 00:03:22.840
you will answer to all my requests.

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:27.759
Only then will I tell you
where Su Hua is.

00:03:30.380 --> 00:03:32.900
(Xiao Yun,
First Master of the Xiao family)

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:05.159
(Su Man'er, Second Madam of the Xiao family)
I'm Su Man'er, the Second Master's wife.

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:07.599
Seeing you today,

00:04:08.439 --> 00:04:10.120
I think we'll get along well.

00:04:15.599 --> 00:04:17.079
Su Hua.

00:04:17.800 --> 00:04:20.120
(Xiao Ye, Second Master of the Xiao family)
Come hither, girl.

00:04:41.879 --> 00:04:43.480
She's nothing but a courtesan,

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:46.360
yet she dares to put on airs with me.

00:05:02.540 --> 00:05:05.340
(Madam Xiao, Grand Madam Xiao)

00:05:08.839 --> 00:05:09.560
Grand Madam Xiao,

00:05:09.759 --> 00:05:10.800
Su Hua isn't pregnant.

00:05:18.639 --> 00:05:19.439
Bury her.

00:05:35.920 --> 00:05:37.160
Help me.

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:40.680
I'm Hua.

00:05:43.399 --> 00:05:44.600
Help me.

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:07.759
(What Su Hua once suffered,)

00:06:08.879 --> 00:06:10.360
(I'll repay with your fear and cries)

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:12.920
(in the days to come.)

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:17.680
What's wrong with you?

00:06:18.439 --> 00:06:20.360
Bride, you should greet the elder.

00:06:21.759 --> 00:06:22.560
Please.

00:06:24.500 --> 00:06:26.340
(Madam Zhang, Aunt)

00:06:33.519 --> 00:06:34.160
All right.

00:06:48.079 --> 00:06:49.240
If you won't greet the elder,

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:50.160
where are you going?

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:52.480
You!

00:06:53.720 --> 00:06:54.959
A good dog doesn't block the way.

00:06:55.160 --> 00:06:56.360
A good donkey doesn't bray.

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:13.439
What are you doing here?

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:15.399
Qing Yan,

00:07:16.519 --> 00:07:18.439
if you want the title
of being a general's wife,

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:19.519
I'll give it to you.

00:07:19.959 --> 00:07:21.360
If you want to live
in the Xiao Residence,

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.279
I'll allow it.

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:24.000
Just one thing.

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:28.720
(Memorial Tablet of Mother, Mo Mei)
You mustn't touch my mother's tablet

00:07:28.839 --> 00:07:30.480
in this ancestral hall,

00:07:31.439 --> 00:07:33.040
or I'll kill you.

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:36.959
You shed blood on the frontier

00:07:37.560 --> 00:07:39.319
and swear to defend the land

00:07:39.519 --> 00:07:41.079
with your life,

00:07:41.439 --> 00:07:43.279
never to yield.

00:07:43.920 --> 00:07:45.959
To have raised such a son,

00:07:46.759 --> 00:07:48.480
your mother is truly admirable.

00:07:49.319 --> 00:07:51.199
Now that her tablet is here,

00:07:51.639 --> 00:07:52.920
will you bow instead

00:07:53.279 --> 00:07:54.480
to that woman in the hall?

00:07:59.199 --> 00:08:01.519
The merriment and parent
in the front hall are all fake.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:03.879
Only this tablet is real.

00:08:03.940 --> 00:08:05.700
(Memorial Tablet of Mother, Mo Mei)

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:15.560
Everyone calls you the Iron-faced King of Hell
on the battlefield.

00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:16.680
Why?

00:08:17.079 --> 00:08:18.720
You're so easily swayed.

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:24.720
Where's Hua?

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:30.000
Why so anxious?

00:08:30.519 --> 00:08:32.320
We haven't finished the wedding rites.

00:08:33.720 --> 00:08:35.360
Stop speaking in riddles.

00:08:36.559 --> 00:08:37.960
I sent men to investigate.

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:41.399
You're skilled at face-changing

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:44.200
and skinning young women's faces.

00:08:44.279 --> 00:08:45.480
What did you do to Hua?

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:51.200
Did you kill her?

00:08:55.879 --> 00:08:57.720
Why say I killed her?

00:08:58.679 --> 00:08:59.960
Why not that I saved her?

00:09:01.720 --> 00:09:04.919
A hairpin has one prong,
a hair fork has two.

00:09:06.240 --> 00:09:08.360
If the heart is as firm
as the hairpiece,

00:09:09.559 --> 00:09:11.559
the twain shall meet,
be it in heaven or on earth.

00:09:13.260 --> 00:09:15.820
(One year earlier)

00:09:16.279 --> 00:09:18.159
(Mid-lake Pavilion)
If the heart is as firm as the hairpiece,

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:20.919
the twain shall meet,
be it in heaven or on earth.

00:09:22.039 --> 00:09:23.480
I'll wait for you in Jiangzhou.

00:09:24.279 --> 00:09:25.559
Don't break your word.

00:09:26.759 --> 00:09:28.080
If I killed her,

00:09:28.919 --> 00:09:30.720
why would she have told me

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:31.759
something so personal?

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:38.080
She told you her secret,

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:42.279
and you used it as leverage
to become the general's wife.

00:09:43.720 --> 00:09:45.120
That's not how a friend should be.

00:09:48.879 --> 00:09:50.879
When Miss Su needed you,

00:09:52.080 --> 00:09:53.720
you returned in triumph

00:09:54.159 --> 00:09:55.679
and won the princess's heart.

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:57.480
How glorious.

00:09:58.600 --> 00:09:59.320
And now,

00:09:59.879 --> 00:10:00.720
you worry

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:02.120
about her

00:10:02.759 --> 00:10:04.559
and about why I married you.

00:10:04.879 --> 00:10:05.519
What is it?

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:08.440
Are you afraid

00:10:09.799 --> 00:10:11.639
Miss Su has turned into a vengeful ghost

00:10:12.840 --> 00:10:13.960
and come after you?

00:10:22.399 --> 00:10:23.759
Don't be afraid, Hua.

00:10:25.440 --> 00:10:28.320
I'll take good care of you
for my brother's sake.

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:39.080
You wench!

00:10:49.039 --> 00:10:50.240
What are you up to now?

00:10:55.799 --> 00:10:56.480
Qing Yan.

00:11:02.320 --> 00:11:02.960
Qing Yan.

00:11:03.879 --> 00:11:04.480
Qing Yan.

00:11:04.720 --> 00:11:05.320
Qing Yan.

00:11:24.660 --> 00:11:28.380
♪Mountains and rivers rise and fall♪

00:11:28.380 --> 00:11:31.580
♪The vast sea opens wide♪

00:11:32.580 --> 00:11:35.580
♪Thank you for staying with me♪

00:11:35.580 --> 00:11:39.660
♪To witness all the lights of the world♪

00:11:40.220 --> 00:11:44.420
♪I remember by the old tree in Qing Yan♪

00:11:45.020 --> 00:11:47.460
♪When we first met♪

00:11:48.100 --> 00:11:55.180
♪Looking back, no more words are needed♪

00:11:55.580 --> 00:12:00.060
♪You went left, I went right♪

00:12:00.060 --> 00:12:04.140
♪If we hadn't met,
there'd be nothing to seek♪

00:12:04.820 --> 00:12:08.460
♪In this long, dusty road of life♪

00:12:08.460 --> 00:12:12.060
♪Love and hate poured
in a single jar of wine♪

00:12:12.060 --> 00:12:15.940
♪Whose heart does love truly claim♪

00:12:15.940 --> 00:12:20.260
♪Yet it yields to just one greeting♪

00:12:21.100 --> 00:12:24.460
♪Gentle longing flows into the river♪

00:12:24.460 --> 00:12:30.260
♪When dreams break,
we will guard each other still♪